      Sea Daffodil is obtained from a natural plant the extract helps to even out skin tone and reduce dark spots

      Gentle Bright Technology

      How to Use!

      • Using your fingertips, massage a small amount on the face and neck in an upward circular motion, focusing on areas like the brow and jawline which need more support.
      • Apply twice a day or once a day in the morning.
